    "This raises important questions about the pedagogical impli-cations of integrating AI into academic settings.",
    "Perhaps the true educational value lies not in using AI to replace human effort, but in analysing and critiquing its output as a means to support knowledge acquisition and foster critical evaluation skills.",
    "Petrovska et al., (2024) saw similar outcomes when integrating ChatGPT into software development education.",
    "Learners were asked to examine AI-generated code alongside their own, leading to a higher level of engagement and a deeper understanding of programming concepts (Petrovska et al., 2024).",
    "This process encouraged learners to recognize errors, analyse stylistic choices and improve the code by critically reflecting on the AI's suggestions."
